HEADWORD: Summation
<hw>Sum*ma"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>sommation</ets>. See <er>Sum</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <def>The
act of summing, or forming a sum, or total amount; also, an
aggregate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Of this series no <qex>summation</qex> is possible to a finite
intellect.</q> <rj><qau>De Quincey.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

